      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRE WATER BURN (2) got around the 340m at this track to take a Grade 6 in a respectable 19.45 for a neck victory. Expected to push the clock again here. SCOOBY DANGER (3) goes very well here starting 10 times for four wins and three minors. In the money last time at Launceston (30.07) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 5 length third. Looks suited here and can measure up. AARIELLA'S GIRL (1) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (26.22) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can measure up. JUNEAU REST (4) was strongly fancied last time on the back of some good recent form but could only manage third (30.29) at Launceston. Deserves a win and gets his chance.",
